  "texts": [
    "[43] found that SF significantly increases electrical resistivity and reduces permeability and water absorption, enhancing resistance to harmful ions.",
    "Similarly, Qureshi et al. [48] and Ali et al.",
    "[44] reported improved resistance to chloride ion penetration and reduced water absorption.",
    "Wang et al. [45] observed that high-purity SF decreases porosity and further improves chloride resistance.",
    "Combining SF with materials like nanosilica or MK offers additional benefits."
  ]
